gobblin.writer.partitioner

Interface WriterPartitioner<D>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TimeBasedAvroWriterPartitioner, TimeBasedWriterPartitioner

    public interface WriterPartitioner<D>
    Partitions records in the writer phase. Implementations must have a constructor with signature (State).

      • partitionForRecord

        GenericRecord partitionForRecord(D record)
        Returns the partition that the input record belongs to. If partitionFoRecord(record1).equals(partitionForRecord(record2)), then record1 and record2 belong to the same partition.
        Parameters:
        record - input to compute partition for.
        Returns:
        GenericRecord representing partition record belongs to.
